 class="t m1629 xc5 h51 y1a7f ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How has this lesson changed your view of temperance? </div><div class="t m1f2 x74 h51 yf77 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m13aa xc5 h51 y13bb ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">After studying this week&apos;s lesson, how would you explain </div><div class="t m2f5 xc5 h51 y4fb ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Christian concept of self-control to a curious neighbor? </div><div class="t ma63 x71 h51 y158c ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: True temperance is refusing to use or do any-</div><div class="t m1347 x71 h51 yf99 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thing harmful and using or doing in moderation those things </div><div class="t m690 x71 h51 y1611 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which are good. It is motivated by our love for God and fellow </div><div class="t m4c4 x71 h51 y1f84 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human beings. And we receive the strength for it from our </div><div class="t mc7 x71 h51 y1a46 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavenly Father. </div><div class="t m6c x6f h51 y1470 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Did you give a Thirteenth Sabbath Offering second </div><div class="t m168a x29 h51 yd9e ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quarter of 1987? </div><div class="t m14b0 x66 h51 y1d64 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">If so, you helped to build this girls&apos; dormitory at Nile </div><div class="t m643 x29 h51 y2ac ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Union Academy in Egypt. </div><div class="t me81 x66 h51 y1be8 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The attached fields, not part of an organized divi-</div><div class="t m477 x29 h51 y191a ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sion, are union territories directed from the General </div><div class="t m15b0 x29 h51 y1ca1 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference headquarters. </div><div class="t m32b x66 h51 y1fe2 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Help them again this Thirteenth Sabbath. </div><div class="t m158a xb1 h1cd y1fe2 ff7 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">See back </div><div class="t m1128 x29 h1cd y1d40 ff7 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cover </